item.title: Tryouts 2024
item.description: Our first tryout took place in Prosetin. There were a lot of firsts: We got together for the first time of the season, first time outside, first time with new coaches. It was a productive weekend, working of motion offence and re-learning to not get lost in a lobster trap and avoid middle-school passes.
